%N A015420 Inverse of 1411th cyclotomic polynomial.
%C A015420 Periodic with period length 1411. - _Ray Chandler_, Apr 07 2017
%H A015420 Ray Chandler, <a href="/A015420/b015420.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..2000</a>
%H A015420 <a href="/index/Per#periodic">Index entries for periodic sequences</a>, period 1411.
%H A015420 <a href="/index/Rec#order_1312">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, order 1312.
%H A015420 <a href="/index/Pol#poly_cyclo_inv">Index to sequences related to inverse of cyclotomic polynomials</a>
%p A015420 with(numtheory,cyclotomic); c := n->series(1/cyclotomic(n,x),x,80);
